snippet.title: Kingdom Two Crowns: Dead Lands Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Find out more about Kingdom Two Crowns at: https://www.kingdomthegame.com/
And check out Bloodstained: https://playbloodstained.com/

Dead Lands is a free update to Kingdom Two Crowns. For the first time, players can switch between four new monarchs from Bloodstained: Ritual of the Night, each with a uniquely powerful trait.
